data.description: Welcome to this stunning home located in the desirable Groveland, FL area. With 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a Den downstairs, this home offers ample space and versatility for any lifestyle. Step into the beautiful open floor plan with a bright and airy feel, perfect for entertaining or simply relaxing with loved ones. The kitchen cabinets complemented by granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances, create a stylish modern look that will impress any buyer. This home is a true gem boasting upgraded ceiling fans throughout, providing comfort and energy efficiency. The property's spaciousness is evident right from the 2- car garage, which features a convenient launch zone for your computer and an area to keep things organized and tidy. Outside, you'll find a covered lanai that beckons you to unwind and enjoy the large backyard, which offers tranquility. The absence of direct back neighbors adds an extra layer of peace and quiet. Plus, being in a lakefront community means access to walking trails, fishing, resort style (beach entry) pool with a splash pad, fitness center , a dog park to bring your furry friends and a charming dock with views of the sunset. One remarkable advantage of this home is that is still under the 10-year warranty, making it both a secure and sound investment. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this nearly new home that is still covered by warranty. Experience the best of Groveland living in this exceptional property. Schedule your private showing today!
